title: THE CITY OF TEMECULA “SENIOR TALK” LECTURE SERIES WILL FEATURE DR. ROBIN VARNET, FROM RENEWED ...
text: ( Source : City of Temecula, CA ) TEMECULA, CA - The City of Temecula Community Services Department will present a free ' Senior Talk ' lecture on Monday, October 12 , 2015 from 10:00 am to 11:00 am, at the Mary Phillips Senior Center ( MPSC )
